This script is a simple script which gives MENU of certian tasks.


To run script use sh script name with full path or from local directory of script.



" sh script "

+++++++
 MENU
+++++++

1.change password
2.See the disk space
3.Login to other box using ssh
4.Show all Service running
5.Show all ports opened
6.Show all java apps running
7.Facility to kill a  app
8.Exit


 Enter your Choice [1-8]:

1

 You have choose to change password


 Enter username to change password

root
Changing password for user root.
New password:
BAD PASSWORD: it is based on a dictionary word
Retype new password:
passwd: all authentication tokens updated successfully.

 Enter any key to continue


### Option "1" perform's password change.

+++++++
